# Map Of The Hashmatique

## Description
A Java program that uses a HashMap to store song titles and lyrics.

## Features
- Create a HashMap
- Add 4 songs
- Retrieve lyrics by song title
- Print all songs and lyrics

## File
- MapOfTheHashmatique.java

## How to Run
1. Open Eclipse
2. Create a Java Project named MapOfTheHashmatique
3. Create MapOfTheHashmatique.java
4. Paste the code
5. Run as Java Application